name: CULT COUNTY by Renegade Kid
blurb: From the twisted minds behind the cult hit Dementium, comes a new kind of horror. Will you join the church of the perfect you?

rewards.reward: DESKTOP IMAGE! Receive a Cult County desktop image to creep you out on a daily basis. "Backer" credit included in the game!

EARLY ADOPTER! Get the game! Season Pass of Season One (All 5 Episodes). We\u2019ll send you one download code for the available platform of your choice, at a bargain price! (includes all previous rewards)
GET THE GAME! Season Pass of Season One  (All 5 Episodes). We\u2019ll send you one download code for the available platform of your choice. (includes all previous rewards)
